last_episode_to_air.name: The Crew Builds an Airport Road
last_episode_to_air.overview: When a family can't get to the airport in time on Speed Meister's road, Rubble & Crew has to build a new road before takeoff.

name: Rubble & Crew
overview: Follow Rubble and his pup family as they use their awesome construction vehicles to build and repair whatever the town of Builder Cove needs in high-stakes adventures.

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Bridge
episodes.overview: Rubble and his construction pup family gear up to build a bridge, only to find the villainous Speed Meister has a different idea. It's up to the Rubble & Crew to work together and save the day by building a new, safe bridge to Builder Cove.

episodes.overview: Rubble and the pups work to build a big bike shop in time for the Bike Festival... unless Speed Meister beats them to it!

episodes.overview: The power is out in Builder Cove! When the pups find out a beaver is to blame, they've got to build him a new home to bring the power back.

episodes.overview: When Speed Meister damages the road ahead of the town helper parade, the pups work fast to repave the way.

episodes.overview: With their splash park plans in troubled waters, the pups have to get creative to cool down the town for the summer.

episodes.overview: When Mayor Greatway asks the pups to fix up a house for her Halloween party, they find out this house might be haunted!

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Bat House
episodes.overview: When Rubble & Crew discover some batty visitors at their Fall Festival, the pups must work fast to build the bats a new, safe home.

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Christmas Show
episodes.overview: Happy Holidays from Rubble and Crew and Truffles the pig, stars of Builder Cove's first ever Christmas Show... on ice!

episodes.overview: When their winter day is snow-free, Rubble and Crew work together to make all of Lucas & Lily's snow sledding dreams come true.

episodes.overview: Rubble and Motor come up with crafty construction solutions to fix Farmer Zoe's squirrel problem before the Farm Fair.

episodes.overview: Rubble and Crew decide to go big when Grocer Gabriel wants something special built outside of his grocery store.

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Treehouse
episodes.overview: Park Ranger Rose's tree might be off limits for climbing, unless Rubble and Grandpa can come up with a solution.

episodes.overview: Rubble and Crew are building a feeder for Farmer Zoe's chickens, but when they get loose, it's up to the pups to wrangle their fowl friends.

episodes.overview: When Speed Meister's roller coaster sends a pet playdate out of control, Rubble and Crew save the day with a bigger, better, and safer coaster.

episodes.overview: When a family of bunnies hops onto the soccer field, Rubble & Crew use their construction skills to build a new sport... Bunny Ball!

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Butterfly Garden
episodes.overview: After the pups discover a new kind of butterfly, it flutters away! Will a giant butterfly garden help bring it back?

episodes.name: The Crew Builds Library Treasure Tunnels
episodes.overview: Rubble and Crew's favorite book series has new additions! But when there's no room for them in the library, the pups have to get creative.

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Super Snack Dispenser
episodes.overview: The pups have a surprise just for Rubble - a snack dispenser! But will they finish it before Rubble finds out?

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Hair Salon
episodes.overview: Rubble and Crew build a hair salon just in time for Grandpa Gravel's special photo—until they run into a squirrely shampoo setback!

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Colorful Crystal Show
episodes.overview: Motor and Lily make a shiny discovery worth celebrating with the coolest light show the pups have ever seen!

episodes.overview: Coach Karima asks Rubble and Crew to build a gym for the gymnastics show but when the beam is too high for Lily, the pups must save the day.

episodes.name: The Crew Puts on a Construction Show
episodes.overview: Rubble and Crew decide to build a show on their own when a traveling show can't get to Builder Cove.

episodes.name: The Crew Builds Charger a Super Bed
episodes.overview: Charger has got too much energy to sleep; Rubble and Crew knows there's always a construction solution.

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Super Squirrelly Whirly Playground
episodes.overview: Rubble and the pups build Mix, Motor, Lucas, and Lily a Super Squirrelly Whirly playdate.

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Smoothie Shop
episodes.overview: Café Carl opens up a smoothie shop on the boardwalk! But when the coaster causes coconut chaos, Rubble & Crew know just what to do.

episodes.overview: Rubble & Crew work together to find a construction solution when Charger's bouncy birthday surprise needs a lift.

episodes.overview: Rubble & Crew want to give Grocer Gabriel the best beach day ever, including a ride on a brand new Ferris wheel at the boardwalk.

episodes.overview: When Farmer Zoe's animals need some relaxation, the pups build a perfect place to practice yoga with Coach Karima.

episodes.overview: Mayor Greatway asks Rubble & Crew to build something special for her friend Mr. Ducky Doo.

episodes.overview: Rubble & Crew work to build a rain tank for Farmer Zoe before a storm, until a chicken complication crops up.

episodes.overview: When Speed Meister builds his own station for reusing trash, the pups have to clean up the mess all over Builder Cove.

episodes.overview: After a baby duckling follows them home, Rubble & Crew use their construction know-how to bring the duckling back to its home.

episodes.overview: When Rubble's favorite baseball star Aaron Judge can’t get out of town to participate in a home run derby, Rubble & Crew build a ballpark to hold the derby right in Builder Cove.

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Surf Bridge
episodes.overview: Surf's up for Rubble & Crew! Well, if they can get over the super hot sand, it is.

episodes.name: The Crew Builds a Pizza Parlor
episodes.overview: Mayor Greatway needs a lot of pizzas; when Speed Meister helps, the pups have to fix his pizza problem.

episodes.name: The Crew Builds an Airport Road
episodes.overview: When a family can't get to the airport in time on Speed Meister's road, Rubble & Crew has to build a new road before takeoff.
